  "title": "Formatting rangeSlider pips with (prefix/suffix)",
  "body": "Hey!\r\n\r\nI'm trying to format the pips in my rangeSlider but cant get it to work.\r\nI've looked a little bit at this https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/1436\r\nBut I am just getting \"Function wNumb not definied\", and i dont know what should be inside this function.\r\n\r\nI've managed to format the tooltips like this:\r\n```\r\ntooltips: {\r\n      format: function(rawValue) {\r\n            return '$' . rawValue;\r\n      }\r\n},\r\n```\r\nHowever, If i am doing similar to the Pips, its not working. Any ideas on how i can do this?",
